        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Surveillance et évaluation du risque de torsade de pointes ou syndrome de QT long syncopal associé à l'exposition médicamenteuse en situation réelle de traitement."
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "Surveillance and assessment of the risk of torsades de pointes or syncope in long QT syndrome from drug exposure during actual treatment."
